      "value": "<p>Beginning at 1st level, your connection to the plane of absolute order allows you to equalize chaotic moments. When a creature you can see within 60 feet of you is about to roll a d20 with advantage or disadvantage, you can use your reaction to prevent the roll from being affected by advantage and disadvantage.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
